This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-elimo layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: git@github.com:linux-sunxi/meta-sunxi.git
  branch: kirkstone

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-elimo layer to the github repo as a PR.

Maintainer: Matteo Scordino <matteo@elimo.io>

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-elimo layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-elimo layer to your build
=================================================

Add the meta-sunxi layer first, then un 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-elimo'

II. Misc
========

This is the BSP layer for the Elimo Initium EVK, based on the Elimo Impetus SoM.

You can use this as:
- a layer to build an image for the Initum EVK itself
- a template to create a BSP layer for your custom board based on the Elimo Impetus SoM
